item.description:
Explosion - Hip Hop - Royalty Free Music by Vodovoz Music Productions. The original video may be found here: https://youtu.be/tRgxZ7Bs8GM. The play along is for any high / low drum. It could be a djembe with bass & slap, or tubanos, or bongos, or any combination of high & low drums.
If you found this video useful please subscribe. If you want to be notified of future videos please click on bell next to subscribe.
